month that it had information to the effect that South Africa
would be hit by a power shortage to be caused by increasing
domestic, commercial and industrial usage of the commodity.
</P>
<P>
The regional grouping advised Zambia, which it said has great
potential to provide power to the entire region, to exploit the
situation and provide South Africa with electricity. 
