<HEADLINE> Russian President to Visit China in Summer </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 1 (Xinhua) -- Russian President Vladimir Putin
will visit China this summer, Chinese Foreign Ministry spokeswoman
Zhang Qiyue announced here today.
</P>
<P>
Zhang told a regular press conference that Chinese and Russian
leaders are expected to exchange views on issues of mutual
interest during Putin's China trip.
</P>
<P>
"The exact date of the visit is still under consultation," she
added. 
</P>
