<HEADLINE> Netherlands Ousts Servette of Switzerland 4-0 in Soccer </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, May 31 (Xinhua) -- Netherlands whitewashed Servette of
Switzerland 4-0 in a friendly Soccer match here on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Patrick Kluivert opened the scoring in the 20th minute for
Netherlands and his teammate Clarence Seedorf added the second 15
minutes later.
</P>
<P>
After the interval, Roy Makaay and Jimmy Floyd Hasselbaink
scored one goal each in the 76th and final minute respectively.
</P>
