<P>
ADDIS ABABA -- Ethiopian Prime Minister Meles Zenawi announced
Wednesday that Ethiopia's war against Eritrea was over after
Ethiopia has "liberated" all its territories lost to Eritrea in
their two-year border conflict.
</P>
