Khabuseyeva, the assistant mayor, died at about 6:30 p.m. local
time (0230 GMT) when their car was hit by two remote-controlled
landmines and came under automatic gun fire along a road linking
Grozny and Urus-Martan. (Russia-Chechnya-Envoy)
